   Financing a Business
     __________________________________________________________________



   Money with a money clip.

   The links on this page provide information about financing your
   business. The main sources of information are the U.S. Business
   Advisor* and the Small Business Administration (SBA)*.

   Quick Links

   U.S. Business Advisor
     Loan Guarantees
     Equity Capital
     Disaster Loans
     Trade Financing
     Industry Finance Resources
     Surety Bond Guarantees

